cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: QUIC Implementations Performance Dataset
abstract: This dataset contains performance measurements of various QUIC client-server
  implementations under controlled network conditions. Experiments involved transferring
  files across different bandwidth limits and file sizes using specific QUIC versions.
  The methodology included executing compiled binaries with defined parameters for
  each run, capturing timing metrics during data transfer. Evaluation was performed
  by comparing logs to compute goodput and success rates, generating visualizations
  like box plots from JSON summaries.
